Player_test00: Tests bet function.  Player should bet minimum when count is
               less than 2.  Player should bet 2*minimum when count is
               greater than 2. 

Player_test01: Tests bet function with various bankrolls/minimums.  Player should
               never bet more than the bankroll or less than the minimum.

Player_test02: Tests draw function.  Tests soft count conditions.

Player_test03: Tests draw function hard count conditions.

Player_test04: Tests expose function with every card to make sure it modifies
               count appropriately.

Player_test05: Tests shuffled().  Count should reset to 0 when shuffled() is
               called.
